# Frontend

- Use existing `components/ui` and `components/common` first.
- Keep API access in `lib/api` and composables.
- Handle loading, success, and error states.
- Use `@/` imports inside `apps/web`.
- Do not fetch the API directly from views when `@app/api-client` can be used.
